title: #92Noon! Gleeman/Neal/Russo
description: #92Noon is back after a long weekend! Aaron Gleeman is in studio to talk Twins! More in-studio Twins talk with the Star Tribune's LaVelle E Neal III as well! Plus, Russo Radio addresses the Phil Kessel controversy!
